description: Cocokind’s sensitive skin-friendly Vitamin C Glow Serum gently brightens, improves uneven skin tone, and visibly boosts skin’s glow. Formulated with ascorbyl glucoside, a stable form of vitamin C, and azelaic acid, this fragrance-free serum brightens the overall appearance of dull, dry skin. Sea grape caviar extract and hyaluronic acid restore hydration and help plump and soften skin over time. This lightweight, vegan serum also delivers a dose of antioxidants that help keep skin looking youthful and bright. The result is healthier-looking, brighter, more even-toned skin. Vitamin C Glow Serum should be applied after cleansing AM and/or PM and can be worn alone for bright, glowy skin or layered with other cocokind serums and creams for added hydration and moisture. Cocokind products are cruelty free. Packaging is made from glass, please recycle it!

Superior Hypoallergenic Microfleece: The skin is the largest organ in the body so treat it right with our Cozy Ultra-Soft Sherpa bed blanket. Featuring a velvety, fuzzy feel that is soft to the touch, our blanket is anti-pilling, wrinkle free, hypoallergenic, and does not shed. Perfect for those prone to allergies! Well, I really can’t say anything about the elastic not holding up because I am wearing them for the first time. But, the length is perfect for me. I prefer lounge pants to “hit” the floor, and these just barely hit the floor. So I’m good on the length! I can tell you they are thin/lightweight, but I live on the Mississippi Gulf Coast and it does get rather hot down here. Just to let you know, I’m about 5’ 7 1/2”, 140ish pounds, and my inseam is 32”. The bottom of the pants are extremely wide. Wider than other Palazzo Pants I’ve ordered in the past. But that doesn’t bother me at all. I ordered a large, size 12, due to what the women in our family calls the Eden tummy, and they fit great! What’s the “Eden tummy” you ask? ALL the women, no matter if they had children or not, got stuck with a bigger tummy. Eden was my grandmother’s maiden name. Now you know what an “Eden tummy” is. Anyway, I bought 4 colors, Navy, Black, Light Gray, and Teal, and after I washed them, they did NOT shrink. description: OLD BAY Gluten Free Classic Seafood Seasoning, 6 oz Can. There are two things you need to know about OLD BAY Seasoning: 1. It’s great on seafood. 2. It’s great on everything else! OLD BAY’s unique blend of 18 herbs and spices was born along the Chesapeake Bay over 75 years ago. Today, it’s won over hearts (and mouths!) across the USA. Marylanders can’t imagine crab without it. They’re shaking and stirring it straight into low country boils down south, and all around the country, folks are getting creative, pairing OLD BAY with pizza, popcorn, donuts, veggies, burgers and fries to name a few. This OLD BAY Classic Seafood Seasoning is in a Plastic can that is 6 ounces. Store this shelf-stable item at an ambient temperature.
product_name: OLD BAY Gluten Free Classic Seafood Seasoning, 6 oz Can
other_attributes: [{"name":"Instructions","value":"Tips:Season burgers & chicken & seafood.Sprinkle on fries, corn-on-the-cob & everything.Toss on wings, pasta & popcorn."},{"name":"Safe Handling Instructions","value":"DO NOT USE IF SEAL UNDER LID IS BROKEN OR MISSING"}]
customer_reviews:
[{"name":"chi███npi███","rating":5,"review":"It’s easy to see why Old Bay has been popular for over 75 years, and why it appears on restaurant tables next to the salt and pepper. Its blend of flavors enhances anything just needing a little extra zing. Its primary ingredient is celery salt, with spices, including red and black pepper, and paprika. There’s just enough heat from the red pepper that makes it spicy, but not too spicy. My favorite use for it is instead of a dry rub on pork ribs, chicken or other grilled or roasted meats (try it on roast turkey!), and it’s an absolutely indispensable ingredient in a Low Country Boil (crab, shrimp, sausage, corn on the cob, pearl onions, potatoes). It’s an excellent flavor addition to macaroni or potato salad, guacamole, deviled or scrambled eggs, baked potatoes, dips, clam chowder, tomato juice, and even popcorn – and of course simple boiled or steamed crab, lobster, shrimp or scallops. Eating healthy? Sprinkle a little Old Bay on half an avocado or spread the avocado and Old Bay on toasted bread. Low-sodium, “hot”, blackened, garlic/herb and lemon/herb versions are also available, as well as a prepared tartar sauce. There’s virtually no limit to its uses and I therefore highly recommend it.","title":"Classic Chesapeake Bay Seafood Seasoning"},{"name":"h22o","rating":5,"review":"It just so happened my wife had just made a batch of chicken salad and I had "Old Bay"seasoning to add to it. These folks have been making this seasoning for 75+ years now...main ingredients celery salt, red and black pepper, paprika and this secret ingredient of mixed spices which makes one of the best seasonings for Poultry,Seafood, Meats and salads....so as you can see by the pictures, I dusted my chicken salad sandwiches... and her ritz crackers with "Old Bay" and what a nice spicy taste with a hint of celery to the taste...I will always have this spice on hand...it's a great addition to your spice rack plus there are some great recipes and tips, on the can that are helpful in adding a great spice to your next meal...","title":"75 years and going strong..."},{"name":"ble███","rating":5,"review":"I've always known that Old Bay is great for steamed shrimp. But, I wanted to try it on other things. Well, let me tell you, I now love it on chicken. Just sprinkle it on and bake it or... how ever you want to prepare it. It really can be used on anything just like any other seasoning. I also tried it on ground beef. Again, very tasty. I like to make my own mayo and I like to try different seasonings in it. Old Bay is a very unique flavor to try. It is not like any other spice or combination of spices. I would try it on almost anything, I think. And I intend to. I really made use of the tips and recipe ideas printed on the can. They are very useful. I also like that it's in a can, not a glass or plastic bottle or jar. The lid has 3 ways to dispense it: spoon, pour or sprinkle. Great for summer BBQ, too.","title":"Not Just for Shrimp anymore"},{"name":"Mon███23","rating":5,"review":"Old Bay is the classic American seasoning for crab and shrimp boils from the North East to the South. A fish bake, low land boil, or beach side lobster bake just isn't the same without it. But don't miss the chance to sprinkle in potato salad, on grilled beef and chicken. If you like to use seasoned salt, you will love Old Bay.","title":"A classic for a reason"},{"name":"Wah███ah","rating":5,"review":"Old Bay can be used on everything. I put old bay on tuna salad, deviled egg,","title":"OLD BAY"},{"name":"phy███nsc███","rating":5,"review":"I've heard of Old Bay Seasoning for years but never took the occasion to purchase and try it.

I've heard others rave about this seasoning, but as it seemed to be stressed mostly for seafood, and I'm not that big a seafood eater, I passed on it. Then I got my free sample. I have to say that I'm a convert. It boasts being for Seafood, Poultry, Salads and Meats. I've tried it with them all and am impressed. Who would think that a blend of Celery Salt, and spices (including Red Pepper and Black Pepper) and Paprika could be so good? Well I do now!

I first tried adding it to my salad Vinargrette and it was delicious. Then on to adding it into the breading of some fried fish. I even tried it with Fried Green Tomatoes with great results. Next, some fried chicken, and finally some steak. I'm a convert! I can't wait to try it with even more things!

I highly recommend this product","title":"Excellent Seasoning!"},{"name":"rrr███rrr███rrr██████","rating":5,"review":"Old Bay Seasoning
Old Bay seasoning comes in a 6 ounce can which will probably last you a year or more. The seasoning is used for seafood, poultry, Seafood. Meats, Salads, basically everything. On the side of the container is a crab cake recipe. I have made these crabcakes according to this recipe and these are the best Maryland crab cakes I have ever eaten. They also gave you several other recipes for steamed shrimp, spicy marinated chicken, and steamed crabs. Basically you can use the seasoning for anything. I made the Spicy Marinated Chicken recipe on the Old Bay container and used it on a whole chicken tonight and put it in the oven and it was delicious, a little goes a long way. I also used it on a whole baking chicken. Old Bay Seasoning gave the chicken a nice golden brown covering. The chicken was moist and tasted wonderful. When boiling shrimp old bay seasoning in the water adds a delicious taste to the shrimp. This seasoning is made in the USA which is a selling point for me. description: 【Ergonomic Lumbar Support】The ergonomically designed backrest of our ergonomic office chair has prominent lumbar support to fit the spine's natural curvature. The Computer Desk Chair with a high-back brings quality and comfort to any office.       【Comfortable Seat】Ergonomic features an all-elastic premium mesh back and a high-density sponge seat making the mesh office chair a good choice for all-day comfortable office seating. The unique mesh design is skin-friendly and breathable, which keeps you cool all day.       【Space-saving】Flip-up armrests are available and won't be in your way when not in use. The Armrests of the computer chair provide comfortable support for your arms and can be flipped up to save space effectively while not in use.       【Multifunctional Mechanism】The seat height of this 360° Rotating chair could be easily adjusted by the pneumatic adjustment lever, and the adjustment range is 18.5-22.2 inches. Besides, the rocking mode helps you to relax from hard work. They can run smoothly on tile, wooden floors, carpets, and other floorings. The large 5-star base increases stability even at the full height range. The maximum weight capacity is 250 lbs.       【Easy Assembly】The home office chair comes with installation instructions and all necessary hardware& tools. We also offer a video to help you, allowing the office chair installation to be completed within 10-15 minutes.

description: Soft Material: Are you looking for something soft, warm, silky and plush? This reversible sherpa blanket checks all the boxes. It boasts double-layered design that delivers twice the coziness and softness you'd get from an ordinary blanket. Front sideis lined with 270GSM soft faux fur, and the other is crafted from skin-friendly 230GSM sherpa fleece. Reversible design brings your living room a comforting and luxurious vibe.   Modern Design: Adopted advanced printing and dyeing technology, this fleece blanket shines with metallic luster under the light. Flowing wave-like pattern and subtle ruching on the top side give this silky blanket a gentle ripple effect. Elegant and decent texture are fully displayed in this simple and generous design-a perfect pick for your home decor!   Versatile Usages: The luxurious sherpa blanket is perfect for snuggling up on the couch and sofa, wrapping up in front of the fire and adding an extra layer of cozy warmth to your bed. Or, just throw it over your shoulder and wear outside as a stole. Add a dash of luxury to your home with this fluffy and super warn blanket is also a nice option.   Easy Care: Please shake the blanket gently after taking it from the compact package, so as to remove floating lints and make it be more fluffy. Wear-resistant material makes it hold up well in the wash. Machine wash in cold water, line dry. Easy to clean and maintenance for long time use.   Intimate Customer Service: We strive for providing you a satisfactory shopping experience, and pay much attention to your real feelings.If you have any problems,concerns or suggestions, please feel free to tell us. We have professional customer service team to offer round-the-clock online help for you.

description: Bodily changes may occur as you age, which is why it’s important to support your body from the inside with essential nutrients. This tasty liquid multivitamin is formulated to support overall wellness as well as libido support in postmenopausal women.                             When exposed to sunlight, your body naturally produces Vitamin D3 — the same type of Vitamin D included in this formula! Vitamin D is an essential vitamin that supports healthy sleep, normal muscle function, healthy bones, and the immune system.                              Vitamin B12 — here as methyl B12 — supports energy levels and aids in amino acid metabolism, while folate (vitamin B9 as methylfolate) helps the formation of red and white blood cells, cell growth, and proper cell division.              Omega-3 as DHA and omega-9 support cognitive health, cardiovascular health, and immune health.                             Essential trace mineral zinc is important for immune function and skin health, while magnesium supports bone health.              In addition to the many essential and important vitamins and minerals, this specially formulated multivitamin for women 40+ also includes a proprietary botanical blend with herbal ingredients including maca root extract, saw palmetto berry oil, chaste tree berry extract, red clover flower extract, raspberry extract, and lutein flower.                              For Most Lifestyles: Non-GMO | Vegan | Dairy Free | Gluten Free | Soy Free |  Sugar Free* | Made in a GMP Facility | Formulated for female adult women 40+                          *Not a low calorie food

description: Brighten dullness and give skin a radiant glow with Neutrogena Healthy Skin Glow Perfector Pen in shade Fair. This makeup pen from a dermatologist-recommended skincare and beauty brand acts as a lightweight, buildable concealer that is designed to create a radiant and flawless complexion. In just one click, the lightweight concealer acts as a shimmer-free highlighter designed to provide a natural looking glow and reveal a flawless complexion. The click pen dispenses the optimum amount of lightweight liquid concealer, making it easy to use the makeup under eyes, on cheeks, or anywhere else you want to brighten and smooth your complexion. Infused with Pro-Vitamin B5 and Vitamin E, the nourishing concealer offers light coverage for all skin types, comes in a range of natural-looking tones, and is ophthalmologist-tested to be safe for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. The makeup pen is also formulated without parabens, mineral oil or dyes.

They ripped after wearing them a few times in the exact area.  Not sure what’s going on."},"positive":{"rating":5,"review":"I LOVE these capris! They're definitely going to be my "go-to" pants for summer. They're EXACTLY what I needed after wearing my beloved Mammut hiking capris until they were shredded and falling apart. These are as close as I've come to replacing those pants. The design is similar to Mammut, and the fabric is almost identical in weight and weave. AND they cost LESS THAN HALF what I paid for the Mammut pants ten years ago!

I'd been buying Stone Touch Cargo Capris, but they stopped making the style I liked, and the ones that are still available were too large. Ah, well... these X-RAY pants are SO much better!

These are incredibly well designed and made. The seams are strong and the fabric is a perfect weight, heavy enough for working outside and light enough for hot weather. Fabric, seams, snaps, and zipper all seem to be very sturdy. They fit my waist well without the belt, and are roomy in the seat and thigh, allowing for lots of freedom of movement.

I've been wearing them daily, and like them so much that I ordered two more pair!

I prefer some men's pants and shirts because they tend to be more well made, and designed for a wider range of movement than many of the women's, and the pockets are deeper... great for me since I hate carrying a purse. These pockets have snap closures rather than that annoying velcro that sticks to other garments in the laundry, so that's another big plus.

It's also one of the few men's cargo capris that come in a size small enough for me."}}

description: TREAT EVERY NIGHT TO A TOUCH OF FUN AND COMFORT  Total Comfort  Transform any evening into a remarkably comfy affair with our cotton pajama pants! Made using 100% cotton, these sleeping bottoms are supremely soft, comfortably breathable to keep you nice and cool, and completely non-irritating thanks to the jersey knit fabric. And weve designed them in eight sizes to complement your shape. So whether youre beautifully big, prettily petite,  or somewhere in between, youll find perfect-fitting PJs to crown any evening.  Take it Easy  These are the perfect pajamas for those nights when you want to let loose and channel your fun side all while looking incredibly cute! Youll love the stylish plaid patterns, in a choice of fun colors, that injects any evening with a whole lot of cheer. And weve ensured that all the cuteness will remain in great condition by combining the highest quality dyes with premium materials. DESIGNED TO LAST: With superior stitching, perfectly-lined hems, and fabric that washes well, these fun pajamas for women are designed to give you years of use. ENJOY A BEAUTIFUL FIT: Whatever your body size or shape, youll find a comfortable fit from our sizes that range from XS-3X. Love everything about them, I wouldn't change a thing!","title":"So soft! Size up for a loose fit."},{"name":"jen███ax","rating":5,"review":"I was happy to find these, at just under 5'10”, it is often tricky to find great basic long-sleeved shirts like these, that are long enough ESPECIALLY in both the overall length AND the arms, but these in size XL are really great for me, and fit me exactly like the model. That said, I wear a size 6 in Old Navy jeans, and it took going all the way up to size XL to achieve the perfect look (demonstrating the model's representation of the loose, long fit), so bear in mind that you will probably need to size up SEVERAL times to achieve the style shown. What I really love about these shirts, is that they can be put through both the washer and dryer with ZERO shrinkage, and it is very easy to keep them soft and wrinkle-free, the colors are BEAUTIFUL, and imho look even better in person than online. I would absolutely recommend these, but only if you can catch them on sale. They are easy-care, so very soft and comfortable, beautiful, bright fade-free colors with just a touch of stretch, but a teensy bit overpriced if you don't catch them on sale. I imagine it would be a pretty close fit if I ordered my regular size, so if you like them loose and long, then I'd definitely recommend sizing up, but all in all these are a great, soft, all-season (Florida) find, and I'm so happy to have found them!","title":"Great find, size up for the fit shown"},{"name":"Lisa","rating":5,"review":"True to size fitting without being to snugged, so if you like it fitted with a little extra breathing room this is for you.","title":"Nice too"},{"name":"Tanya","rating":5,"review":"Great material fits great"},{"name":"Suz███e","rating":5,"review":"I like the color and fit of this long sleeve t-shirt.
